# This is the TEMPLATE repo's own ignore file. The generated project ships its
# own .gitignore (see template/.gitignore.jinja).

### Python / uv (this template's dev tooling) ###
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
.direnv/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/

### Copier test renders ###
/.copier-test/

### MkDocs (this repo's own docs site — see docs/) ###
site/

### ship continuity files (progress tracking, never committed) ###
.ship/

### superpowers:brainstorming local artifacts (mockups/companions, never committed) ###
.superpowers/

### VS Code — track only the curated workspace files, ignore personal/machine state ###
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

### macOS ###
.DS_Store
